abstract: College Basketball Roundup; Connecticut women's basketball team defeats Nebraska, 88-46, to record its 40th consecutive win; other women's and men's scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Breanna Stewart led top-ranked Connecticut to its 40th consecutive win, 88-46, over visiting Nebraska on Saturday.

headline.main: UConn Women Coast to 40th Straight Win
headline.print_headline: UConn Women Coast to 40th Straight Win
